  token: {{authToken}}
}

body:json {
  {
    "amount": 100
  }
}

docs {
  # Airtime Quote

  Calculates how much the user will pay for an airtime amount.

  ## Endpoint

  `POST /api/v1/services/airtime/quote`

  ## Body Fields

  `amount`
  Required. Airtime value the user wants to buy.

  ## Expected Response

  If airtime markup is `0%`:

  ```json
  {
    "quote": {
      "amount": 100,
      "sellingPrice": 100,
      "profit": 0,
      "markupPercent": 0,
      "roundingMode": "ceil"
    }
  }
  ```

  If airtime markup is `5%`, `sellingPrice` becomes `105`.

  Frontend should display `sellingPrice` as the wallet amount to be deducted.
}
